Class RegionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • param.RegionFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BoxRegionFactory

    abstract class RegionFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to produce new regions of a given subclass of Region.
    Author:
    Ernst Moritz Hahn (University of Oxford)
    See Also:
    RegionFactory
